{
    "thoughts": {
        "text": "I am sorry to hear about your neighbor's condition, and I understand your desire to help solve problems that can make a positive impact on humanity. It is important to have a clear plan and understanding of the resources needed to achieve your goals. I suggest we start by researching potential funding sources and creating a proposal that outlines your goals, methods, and expected outcomes. We can then use this proposal to reach out to potential funders and seek their support.",
        "reasoning": "It is important to have a clear plan and proposal when seeking funding, as it helps to communicate your goals and objectives to potential funders.",
