        "speak": "I am sorry to hear about your neighbor's condition, and I understand your desire to help solve problems that can make a positive impact on humanity. I suggest we start by researching potential funding sources and creating a proposal that outlines your goals, methods, and expected outcomes. We can then use this proposal to reach out to potential funders and seek their support."
    },
